---
import Displaybillede from "../components/Displaybillede.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Insta2 from "../components/Insta2.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.png" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="kontakt os på denne side" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/generel.css" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Hubballi&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Khani</title>
  </head>
  <Header />
  <body>
    <Displaybillede baggrund="/img/kontakt/kontakt.webp" text="KONTAKT" />
    <h1>SKRIV TIL OS</h1>
    <p>Har du spørgsmål til leveringsmuligheder, din ordre eller måske noget tredje? Så er du velkomne til at skrive til os. Vi sidder altid klar til at svare på alle spørgsmål. Vi bestræber os på at besvare dit spørgsmål inden for 1-3 hverdage.</p>

    <div class="container">
      <form action="/action_page.php">
        <div class="grid_1-1">
          <input type="text" id="navn" name="navn" placeholder="NAVN" />
          <input type="text" id="telefon" name="telefon" placeholder="TELEFON" />
        </div>
        <input type="text" id="email" name="email" placeholder="EMAIL" />
        <textarea id="kommentar" name="kommentar" placeholder="KOMMENTAR" style="height:100px"></textarea>

        <input type="submit" value="INDSEND" />
      </form>
    </div>
    <Insta2 />
    <Footer />
  </body>

  <style>
    p {
      max-width: 60ch;
      text-align: left;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: var(--font-size-p);
      line-height: var(--line-height-form);
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 70px 0px;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 650px;
      text-align: center;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    input[type="text"],
    select,
    textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin-top: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      background-color: var(--surface-beige);
      border: none;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    input[type="submit"] {
      background-color: var(--surface-white);
      padding: 14px 70px;
      border: 1px solid var(--surface-black);
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: "Hubballi", cursive;
      font-size: var(--font-size-form);
      margin-top: 70px;
    }

    input[type="submit"]:hover {
      scale: 1.04;
    }

    .grid_1-1 {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      column-gap: 30px;
    }

    #email {
      width: 100%;
      font-family: "Hubballi", cursive;
      font-size: var(--font-size-form);
    }
    #kommentar {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100px;
      resize: none;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-family: "Hubballi", cursive;
      font-size: var(--font-size-form);
    }

    #navn {
      width: 50%;
      font-family: "Hubballi", cursive;
      font-size: var(--font-size-form);
    }
    #telefon {
      width: 50%;
      font-family: "Hubballi", cursive;
      font-size: var(--font-size-form);
    }

    @media (max-width: 1000px) {
      .grid_1-1 {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      #navn {
        width: 100%;
      }
      #telefon {
        width: 100%;
      }

      input[type="text"],
      select,
      textarea {
        margin-top: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .container {
        padding: 35px;
      }

      p {
        padding: 10px;
        font-size: var(--font-size-p);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.3rem;
        margin-bottom: 0px;
      }

      p {
        padding: 35px;
        margin-bottom: 0px;
      }

      .container {
        padding: 0px 30px 30px 30px;
      }

      input[type="submit"] {
        margin-top: 45px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</html>
